Reasoning: The paper deals with visual place recognition, which is a problem in computer vision. The use of CNN-based descriptors and unsupervised learning methods suggests that the paper belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The application of these methods in robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) also makes these sub-categories likely. Finally, the mention of experiments involving image and video data suggests that the paper may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
